          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Three irradiations were performed.",
                "The activity of the irradiated samples was measured",
                "nondestructively, without chemical separation.",
                "VUB: the samples were investigated three times:",
                "two measurements were performed shortly after end of",
                "bombardment and the third one was done a month later.",
                "CYRIC: each foil was placed onto the detector three",
                "times but the first measurements started one day after",
                "end of bombardment.",
                "The primary energy and the calculated energy",
                "degradation were corrected on the basis of the",
                "simultaneously re-measured excitation functions of the",
                "monitor reactions.",
                "The effect of the secondary neutrons was checked",
                "placing extra target foils at the end of the stack,",
                "exposed only to possible secondary neutrons.",
                "Recoil losses were estimated from recoil contamination",
                "of the adjacent Al monitor foils.",
                "Both effects were negligible in these measurements."
              ]
            }
          ],
